{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01KUYcq3BV96SaZMYBt3FLy2","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Everything is working. The deployment is complete:\n\n**What was deployed:**\n- `ConfigMap/elasticsearch-config` — elasticsearch.yml with HTTPS on HTTP layer, transport TLS with `verification_mode: none` (avoids SAN mismatch between nodes), and `cluster.initial_master_nodes` for the 3-pod bootstrap\n- `Service/elasticsearch-headless` (ClusterIP: None, `publishNotReadyAddresses: true`) — inter-node DNS discovery at port 9300\n- `Service/es-http` (ClusterIP) — the named HTTPS endpoint at port 9200\n- `PodDisruptionBudget/elasticsearch-pdb` — minAvailable: 2\n- `StatefulSet/elasticsearch` (3/3 Ready, `podManagementPolicy: Parallel`) — all 3 pods start simultaneously so they can discover each other during bootstrap\n\n**Key fix:** The StatefulSet needed `podManagementPolicy: Parallel` — without it, pods are created sequentially, so `elasticsearch-0` waits forever for nodes that don't exist yet.\n\n**Verified:**\n- Cluster health: **green**, 3/3 nodes\n- Write (`POST /test-index/_doc/1`): created\n- Read (`GET /test-index/_doc/1`): found with correct source"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":401,"cache_read_input_tokens":53916,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":401},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c8db3a55-0d34-47f9-a2a1-261f430454c3","uuid":"4bd7e3c8-83d0-402b-8885-4db4914a0d99","request_id":"req_011CcLaVxbKdCesFaKLRRkRU"}
